ATTRIBUTE.NAME: Post SQL
ATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
UPDATE INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL SET TGT_VAL=( SELECT count(*) FROM STG_MX_ITEM WHERE trunc(UPDATE_TIMESTAMP)= (SELECT MAX(trunc(MAP_RUN_DT)) FROM INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_STG_MX_ITEM' AND MAP_RUN_DT <=SYSDATE)) WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_STG_MX_ITEM' AND MAP_RUN_DT=(SELECT MAX(MAP_RUN_DT) FROM INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_STG_MX_ITEM' AND MAP_RUN_DT <=SYSDATE ) ;
UPDATE INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL SET STATUS_YN = (CASE WHEN SRC_VAL = TGT_VAL THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END ) WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_STG_MX_ITEM' AND MAP_RUN_DT=(SELECT MAX(MAP_RUN_DT) FROM INFO_ETL_CNTL_TBL WHERE INFO_MAP_NAME = 'm_STG_MX_ITEM' AND MAP_RUN_DT <=SYSDATE );
